THE Golden Jubilee hospital in Clydebank has appointed former Glasgow nurse Anne Marie Cavanagh as its new Nurse Director.She said: &quot;Having worked as a nurse for almost 30 years and with experience in senior roles, I feel well equipped to take on this position at this very exciting time.&quot;The Golden Jubilee is committed to developing new and innovative ways to ensure patients receive the highest possible standard of care, so I am really looking forward to helping enhance our already excellent services, which will ensure we continue to provide the safest and highest quality care for all of our patients.&quot;